#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Nakulapituvagga "
msgstr "1. Nakula’s Father "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Kālattayadukkhasutta → dutiyaatītānāgatasuttaṃ (bj) | atītānāgatapaccuppanna 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Kālattayadukkhasutta "
msgstr "10. Suffering in the Three Times "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.20, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ atītānāgataṃ; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form of the past and future is suffering, "

msgctxt "sn22.10:1.3"
msgid "ko pana vādo paccuppannassa. "
msgstr "not to mention the present. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako atītasmiṃ rūpasmiṃ anapekkho hoti; "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple doesn’t worry about past form, "

msgctxt "sn22.10:1.5"
msgid "anāgataṃ rūpaṃ nābhinandati; "
msgstr "doesn’t look forward to enjoying future form, "

msgctxt "sn22.10:1.6"
msgid "paccuppannassa rūpassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti. "
msgstr "and they practice for disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding present form. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.7"
msgid "Vedanā dukkhā … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.8"
msgid "saññā dukkhā … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.9"
msgid "saṅkhārā dukkhā … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.10"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ atītānāgataṃ; "
msgstr "Consciousness of the past and future is suffering, "

msgctxt "sn22.10:1.11"
msgid "ko pana vādo paccuppannassa. "
msgstr "let alone the present. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.12"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako atītasmiṃ viññāṇasmiṃ anapekkho hoti; "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple doesn’t worry about past consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn22.10:1.13"
msgid "anāgataṃ viññāṇaṃ nābhinandati; "
msgstr "doesn’t look forward to enjoying future consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn22.10:1.14"
msgid "paccuppannassa viññāṇassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hotī”ti. "
msgstr "and they practice for disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding present consciousness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.10:1.15"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

